OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FFly-tipper who dumped 51   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ftonnes of tyres in Glasgow 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fjailed                     
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A fly-tipper who dumped 51 tonnes of   
OL,6, tyres on waste ground across Glasgow   
OL,7, has been jailed for 11 months.         
OL,9,FDeclan Clarke, 30, from Dumbarton,     
OL,10,Fcollected tyres from garages for a fee 
OL,11,Fand hired workers and vans to dispose  
OL,12,Fof them in car parks and empty land.   
OL,14,FHe was fly-tipping "on an industrial   
OL,15,Fscale" between June and November 2000, 
OL,16,Fsaid Sheriff John McCormick.           
OL,18,FMost of the tyres were dumped at       
OL,19,FDalsetter Crescent in Drumchapel and   
OL,20,Fconsumed in a fire on 24 July, 2020.   
